| **specs** | 规格金字塔与工作区 | `SpecsStore`, `GoalsTable`, `RelationsPanel`, `AutoLinkContent` | agent-config, chat, relay, ui-system | [模块](specs/module.ad) · [目标](specs/goals.ad) · [架构](specs/architecture.ad) · [设计](specs/designs.ad) · [计划](specs/plans.ad) · [评审](specs/reviews.ad) · [报告](specs/reports.ad) · [测试](specs/tests.ad) |
